About
-----
This plugin for OJS 2 provides an export plugin to generate

License
-------
This plugin is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2. See the file COPYING for the
complete terms of this license.

System Requirements
-------------------
Same requirements as the OJS 2.x core.

Installation
------------
To install the plugin:
 - copy the alm folder into OJS/plugins/importexport

The export functionality can then be accessed only through the command line:
Usage:
php tools/importExport.php AlmExportPlugin [outFileName] [journal_path] all
php tools/importExport.php AlmExportPlugin [outFileName] [journal_path] sinceLast
php tools/importExport.php AlmExportPlugin [outFileName] [journal_path] articles [articleId1] [articleId2] ...
php tools/importExport.php AlmExportPlugin [outFileName] [journal_path] issue [issueId]

Known Issues/Limitations
---------
This plugin only works through the command line. A cronjob needs to be set up to push articles to
ALM. The API to do this has not yet been developed.


